#. type: Title
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-16-quarkus-insights-251-semeru-openj9.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus Insights #251: Faster Startup with IBM Semeru Runtimes and OpenJ9"
msgstr "Quarkus Insights 第 251 期：借助 IBM Semeru 运行时和 OpenJ9 实现更快的启动速度"

#. type: YAML Front Matter: synopsis
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-16-quarkus-insights-251-semeru-openj9.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Mark Stoodley explains how IBM Semeru Runtimes and the Eclipse OpenJ9 JVM deliver faster startup times and lower memory footprint through shared classes cache technology, and how Quarkus makes it easy to take advantage of these benefits."
msgstr "马克·斯图德利（Mark Stoodley）详细阐述了IBM Semeru Runtimes和Eclipse OpenJ9 JVM如何通过共享类缓存技术实现更快的启动速度和更低的内存占用，以及Quarkus如何让开发者轻松利用这些优势。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-16-quarkus-insights-251-semeru-openj9.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This summary was generated using AI, reviewed by humans - https://youtube.com/live/ql0wK79DxtY[watch the video] for the full story."
msgstr "本摘要由人工智能生成，并经人工审核—— link:https://youtube.com/live/ql0wK79DxtY[请观看视频] 了解完整内容。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-16-quarkus-insights-251-semeru-openj9.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Episode 251 of Quarkus Insights explored how developers can achieve faster startup times and reduced memory footprint by using https://developer.ibm.com/languages/java/semeru-runtimes/[IBM Semeru Runtimes] with Quarkus. Mark Stoodley, Chief Architect for Java at IBM and project co-lead for https://www.eclipse.org/openj9/[Eclipse OpenJ9], joined the show to explain the technology behind these performance improvements and how Quarkus has made it trivially easy to take advantage of them."
msgstr "《Quarkus Insights》第 251 期探讨了开发人员如何通过在 Quarkus 中使用 link:https://developer.ibm.com/languages/java/semeru-runtimes/[IBM Semeru 运行时] 来实现更快的启动速度并减少内存占用。 IBM Java首席架构师、 link:https://www.eclipse.org/openj9/[Eclipse OpenJ9项目] 联合负责人Mark Stoodley做客本期节目，详细阐述了这些性能提升背后的技术原理，以及Quarkus如何让开发者能够轻松利用这些优势。"

